                                    &lt;h2&gt;Responsive layout site&lt;/h2&gt;
                                    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsive layout of the website&lt;/strong&gt; - this is a common layout, plus a built-in stylesmedia queries in which your site will look good on your PC and on your tablet or mobile phone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previously, the mobile version does a completely different site, but recently there was a technology called (Responsive Design), and using it can be done at one site so that it works on all devices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsive layout  of the website&lt;/strong&gt; - it is a great alternative to the rubber as rubber structure of the site is mainly suitable for PC and is not suitable for other digital devices.&lt;/p&gt;
